{"tid":497851,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都好唔中意人地冇所謂","createTime":"2017-12-13T08:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T11:42:09.000Z","uid":116035,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bd38abf30f05b06e23479d2bd1f2bcb81897e6c8","tid":497851,"uid":116035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"首先岀食街食飯，食乜都冇所謂<br />\n問你想做乜，又答冇所謂<br />\n最嬲係，有時始終會有d野係自己介意<br />\n想同人呻下既時候，佢身為局外人唔關佢事<br />\n佢就會話冇所謂啦，咁認真做乜<br />\n其實每個人都有自己既執著，同你講可能係想聽下啲意見或者抒發下<br />\n點知收翻黎既得句冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be03ef57a4514d7a57ab605c472f6eee51fd7d1b","tid":497851,"uid":116035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387e03844a122876ec9e9c5aead98cc720995f56","tid":497851,"uid":83606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦"},{"pid":"56a57dbfae02d5a3f2050442e52260966e1da84f","tid":497851,"uid":134789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"冇所䜊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b05ae33256dbc795c5ab6bdb8e2a163b09312ef","tid":497851,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"有咩好講啫，無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e10e823094493d054d41fa2eac887905904e500","tid":497851,"uid":116035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"算，反正都預左你地會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158d0097ad6baa23589a9e418cc7fe5dcbacaa3c","tid":497851,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"30c032f77d68472b0816394cbd3985dc78ebf866","tid":497851,"uid":37153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"人地話冇所謂你咪渣主意囉 到時食啲佢唔想食既都係佢既事<br />\n你都識講人地係局外人 你講啲野關人撚事咩"},{"pid":"7766570c1e1297fc33691a7fd1c9084116f9b4e6","tid":497851,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deeba4eda897cd3880e04f8447ccd1ab1feb4d9f","tid":497851,"uid":31419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"有好多時我問人都係想有意見<br />\n但多數都係同我講無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8963593b130a6b6b5976314981e97e6b78c1fc","tid":497851,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂姐"},{"pid":"b701491be2d22d717dc55bc8eb5d7add2c8e67e7","tid":497851,"uid":140145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"求其啦"},{"pid":"cc839481d1c8df08e890b2fca7264f8b78d5d6ad","tid":497851,"uid":116035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有好多時我問人都係想有意見<br />\n但多數都係同我講無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他人比唔到意見，首先係佢地本身唔在乎樣野，其次係佢地根本唔明白，呢個時候真係野都廢事同佢地講"},{"pid":"d9776556a84459b02ba75a6f4fb9564885e81e20","tid":497851,"uid":45627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"出街食飯話冇所謂唔緊要<br />\n最緊要係唔好講完冇所謂但又嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你搵佢呻, 對方都可以答你冇所謂<br />\n先唔諗佢真hea定真係想叫你睇開啲<br />\n巴打你反感都証明你地唔啱傾心事<br />\n既然係咁咪搵過第二個傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8c63db43187a2dc7b39c26b07a52474365fb3d","tid":497851,"uid":116035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出街食飯話冇所謂唔緊要<br />\n最緊要係唔好講完冇所謂但又嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你搵佢呻, 對方都可以答你冇所謂<br />\n先唔諗佢真hea定真係想叫你睇開啲<br />\n巴打你反感都証明你地唔啱傾心事<br />\n既然係咁咪搵過第二個傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我即刻同佢off topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢事嘈交"}]}